<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="prevent-vt">prevent <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /prɪ'vent/    美 /prɪ'vent/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>阻止；预防；防止：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In this way we prevented the spread of this disease.
我们用这种方式防止了这种疾病的蔓延。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="prevent-sb-sth-from-doing-sth">prevent sb / sth (from) doing sth:</h3>
<p>1.****  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There were many ways to prevent this from happening.
有多种方法可以防止此事发生。</p><footer> 2008 广东改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Pollution prevents people from seeing objects in the sky that they could see quite easily in the past. 
污染使人看不到在过去很容易看到的天空中的物体。</p><footer>2013 天津改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>prevention /prɪ'venʃn/ n [U]  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Prevention is better than cure.
预防胜于治疗。</p></div></div>